derer-ejs <span class="comment">--save</span></span><br><span class="line">$ npm <span class="keyword">install</span> hexo-renderer-stylus <span class="comment">--save</span></span><br><span class="line">$ npm <span class="keyword">install</span> hexo-renderer-marked <span class="comment">--save</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>#2、中文乱码</p><p>解决方案：将md文件和yml文件的格式设置为UTF-8</p>]]></content>
    
